# AI for Identity & Access Management (AI-IAM)
An enterprise AI assistant that helps Microsoft Identity engineers investigate authentication issues, explain security policies, 
analyze identity risks, and automate repetitive IAM tasks using Microsoft Graph, PowerShell, and AI.

# Architecture
             IAM Engineer
                   │
      "Investigate user"
                   │
                   ▼
        AI Orchestrator
                   │
        ┌──────────┴──────────┐
        ▼                     ▼
 Microsoft Graph         Knowledge Base
        ▼                     ▼
 Sign-ins             Microsoft Learn
 Users                Company Docs
 Groups               GitHub Docs
 CA Policies          Best Practices

        └──────────┬──────────┘
                   ▼
         AI Reasoning Engine
                   ▼
 Investigation Report
                   ▼
        Engineer Reviews
                   ▼
          Optional Action
